{"tid":2127920,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞和街街市男子拒戴口罩  食環署首次按599I提出檢控","createTime":"2020-07-27T14:57:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T03:50:16.000Z","uid":7439,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ce00e3ede32ad0eee4160bd147dfcc65176147db","tid":2127920,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T14:57:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/18485709_1753503771342871_7447803784230920315_n.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=zrWjL3vd3C8AX-7u2xh&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=1d3983db7b6cc6451e36ecc8384e262e&amp;oe=5F45F1D9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F18485709_1753503771342871_7447803784230920315_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3DzrWjL3vd3C8AX-7u2xh%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3D1d3983db7b6cc6451e36ecc8384e262e%26oe%3D5F45F1D9&h=2ec38f0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202007/27/P2020072700677.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202007%2F27%2FP2020072700677.htm&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpT4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=4bb44797\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202007/27/P2020072700677.htm</a><br />\n<em>食環署向違反《預防及控制疾病（佩戴口罩）規例》（第599I章）人士提出檢控<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  食物環境衞生署（食環署）今日（七月二十七日）表示，三名人士因在街市範圍內沒有佩戴口罩，違反《預防及控制疾病（佩戴口罩）規例》（第599I章）（《規例》）的有關規定被檢控。<span class=\"red\">這是食環署首次控告違反《規例》有關規定人士。</span><br />\n<br />\n  食環署發言人表示，自《規例》有關在室內地方須佩戴口罩的規定實施後，食環署已加強巡查轄下街市，確保有關人士遵照相關規定。食環署人員今日進行巡查時，發現兩名分別在北河街街市及土瓜灣街市的檔戶，<span class=\"red\">及一名送貨到瑞和街街市的男子在街市範圍內沒有佩戴口罩，經勸喻無效後，食環署人員遂檢控該三名人士。</span><br />\n<br />\n  根據《規例》，任何人未有按規定佩戴口罩即屬犯罪，<span class=\"red\">最高可處罰款五千元或被定額罰款二千元。</span><br />\n<br />\n  發言人說：「為保障街市檔戶及市民的健康及安全，本署呼籲市民須遵照《規例》相關規定，在街市範圍內佩戴口罩。本署會繼續加強巡查及執法行動，確保有關人士遵照相關規定。」<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年7月27日（星期一）<br />\n香港時間21時00分</em>"},{"pid":"e3e74e0fe90a08c829b98569ddbe1a518b6b32d3","tid":2127920,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T14:57:20.000Z","msg":"曾有確診或疑似2019冠狀病毒病個案的大廈名單資料庫<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chp.gov.hk/files/pdf/building_list_chi_20200726.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chp.gov.hk%2Ffiles%2Fpdf%2Fbuilding_list_chi_20200726.pdf&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpT4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=55a885af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chp.gov.hk/files/pdf/building_list_chi_20200726.pdf</a><br />\n<blockquote>觀塘 瑞和街市政大廈 17/07/2020 2124<br />\n觀塘 瑞和街市政大廈 19/07/2020 1512, 1672, 1802,<br />\n1884</blockquote>"},{"pid":"aaab3eecd19dcd417f9c64f3bd2ea07f43efdc34","tid":2127920,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T14:57:30.000Z","msg":"梁凱晴：唔該瑞和街啲人戴返口罩好唔好？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fHDGyS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fHDGyS</a><br />\n<br />\n瑞和街市政大廈失守  患者(#1512)曾至大家樂、龍慶堂(有先人牌位)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2107853\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2107853</a><br />\n<br />\n瑞和街糧食店被罰暫停營業十四天<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1697001</a><br />\n<br />\n瑞和街掃違例泊車 揭運魚車司機停牌駕駛<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1186592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1186592</a>"},{"pid":"3d74e39f3eae88c0f30467102fe38418b09a599e","tid":2127920,"uid":63675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T14:58:15.000Z","msg":"xben"},{"pid":"f009a454fdcc9e9cfc254d1c80ea68eeac557ea8","tid":2127920,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T14:59:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/109727985_583761422508648_1690915620602248148_o.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=SQ80Id6Q8a0AX9